"      Imuprin (AE, BB, BF, BH, BJ, BM, BS, BZ, CI, CY, EG, ET, FI, GH, GM, GN, GY, HK, IQ, IR, JM, JO, KE, KW, LB, LR, LY, MA, ML, MR, MU, MW, NE, NG, OM, PR, QA, SA, SC, SD, SL, SN, SR, SY, TH, TN, TT, TW, TZ, UG, YE, ZM, ZW);",
